# Filament Resource Structure Plan

## Overview
The Admin Panel will manage Users, Learning Content (Classes/Courses), and AI Assessment Data.

## 1. User Management
### Resources
- **UserResource**: Standard user management.
    - **Fields**: Name, Email, Role (Enum: Admin, Teacher, Student), Avatar.
    - **Relations**: `hasMany` Classes (as Teacher), `hasMany` Enrollments (as Student).
- **RoleResource** (Optional if using Spatie Permission): To manage granular permissions.

## 2. Learning Management System (LMS)
### Resources
- **ClassResource** (or CourseResource):
    - **Fields**: 
        - Title (Text)
        - Slug (Text, Auto-generated)
        - Description (RichEditor)
        - Thumbnail (ImageUpload)
        - Price (Money, Nullable for Free)
        - Status (Select: Draft, Published, Archived)
        - Level (Select: Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced)
    - **Relations**: `belongsTo` Teacher (User).
- **ModuleResource** (or ContentResource):
    - **Fields**:
        - Class ID (Select, Filterable)
        - Title (Text)
        - Type (Select: Video, PDF, Quiz, Text)
        - Content (RichEditor or FileUpload)
        - Duration (Number, minutes)
        - Sort Order (Number)

## 3. Hero AI & Assessments
### Resources
- **AssessmentResultResource**:
    - **Purpose**: View-only resource to monitor AI assessment results.
    - **Fields**:
        - User (Relation)
        - Type (Select: VAK, SWOT, RIASEC, MULTIPLE_INTELLIGENCE)
        - Result Data (KeyValue or JSON View) - stores the raw AI findings.
        - Created At (DateTime)
    - **Widgets**: Charts showing distribution of Learning Styles (VAK) across all students.

## 4. Try Out / Exams (Future)
### Resources
- **ExamResource**:
    - **Fields**: Title, Description, Duration, Passing Grade.
    - **Relations**: `hasMany` Questions.
- **QuestionResource**:
    - **Fields**: Question Text, Type (Multiple Choice, Essay), Options (Repeater), Correct Answer.

## Implementation Notes
- Use **Filament Panels** to separate logic:
    - `/admin`: Super Admin & Staff.
    - `/teacher`: Teachers managing their classes.
    - `/student`: (Optional) If not using custom Blade/Livewire frontend for dashboard.
- **Theme**: Register a custom Filament theme to use the primary color `#DC2626` (Red-600).
- **Navigation**: Group resources by "LMS", "Users", and "Analytics".
